draw_text(info2_x, info2_y, "Volkmusik refers to a collection of related styles of traditional folk\nmusic from the Alpine regions of Germany, Austria, and\nSwitzerland. This type of folk music focuses on the lifestyle of\nAlpine farmers and peasants, often incorporating regional\ndialects. The most distinctive instruments volkmusik features\nare the alpenhorn, a long curved horn, the accordion, and\nthe undulating singing style known as yodelling.");